android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to change the state of network connectivity.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows an application to disable the key lock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the key lock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the key lock when the call is finished.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY.description: Allows an application to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Malicious applications can make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.

android.permission.READ_PROFILE.info: read the user's personal profile data
android.permission.READ_PROFILE.description: Allows an application to read the user's personal profile data.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to use the account authenticator capabilities of the Account Manager, including creating accounts as well as obtaining and setting their passwords.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTER.description: Permission an application must hold in order to use

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.description: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOC.description: Allows an app to access location in the background. If you're requesting this permission, you must also request either

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

com.huawei.android.launcher.permission.W.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

com.oppo.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTI.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

App has a Network Security Configuration
[android:networkSecurityConfig]
manifest_analysis.desc: The Network Security Configuration feature lets apps customize their network security settings in a safe, declarative configuration file without modifying app code. These settings can be configured for specific domains and for a specific app.
manifest_analysis.name: App has a Network Security Configuration [android:networkSecurityConfig]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.ncl.bge.common.controller.PopupActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.google.android.gms.measurement.AppMeasurementInstallReferrerReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.INSTALL_PACKAGES
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

"child_access_confirmation_legal_copy" : "ノルウェージャンクルーズライン（以下、「ノルウェージャン」）は、携帯電話やデバイスにダウンロードできるモバイルアプリ（以下、「アプリ」）を提供しています。 このアプリはユーザーの情報を収集します。 ノルウェージャンクルーズラインは、%1$d歳未満のお子様のご両親または法定後見人がこの保護者同意書に署名することをそのお子様のアプリ利用の条件としています。

 1. お客様は、下に示された%2$d歳未満のお子さまの親または法的後見人であることを確認し、同意するものとします。

 2. このフォームの記入、署名、返却により、お客様はお客様のお子さまによるアプリの利用、この文書およびノルウェージャンクルーズラインの個人情報保護方針（https://www.ncl.com/about-us/privacy-policy）に基づいてアプリならびにノルウェージャンクルーズラインが実行する、アプリを通じたお子さまの個人情報の収集、利用および/または開示に同意するものとします。

 3. さらに、アプリの利用はすべて、アプリの利用規約/サービス規約、ノルウェージャンクルーズラインがアプリの使用に適用するその他いかなる規約、規則、方針にも従うものとします。

 4. アプリは通信機能（チャットや船内通話など）を備えていることにご注意ください。 アプリを使用して通信する場合、アプリの電話番号は相手に表示されません。 お子様が、親御様または法的保護者の方の同意を得ずに、アプリの電話番号を他者に知らせることがないようお伝えください。

 5. お子様がデバイスを使用して船外へ通話をすることもできますが、その場合は料金または手数料が発生しますのでご注意ください。モバイルデバイスを使用して船外に通話した場合、その料金または手数料はステートルームに請求されます。

 6. アプリにはデータ解析機能があり、ノルウェージャンクルーズラインはその機能を、独自の裁量で（個人情報保護方針に従い）任意の方法で使用します。これには、ノルウェージャンクルーズラインのサービス、アプリのパフォーマンス、およびお客様の体験の改善、またはその他の用途が含まれますが、それらに限定されません。"

"child_access_confirmation_legal_copy" : "Norwegian Cruise Line („Norwegian“) stellt eine mobile Applikation (die „App“) zur Verfügung, die auf ein Mobiltelefon oder ein mobiles Gerät heruntergeladen werden kann. Die App sammelt Daten über seine Benutzer. Norwegian erfordert, dass die Eltern oder Erziehungsberechtigten von Kindern unter %1$d dieses Einverständnisformular für Eltern als Bedingung für die Nutzung der App durch das Kind unterzeichnen.

 1. Sie bestätigen und stimmen zu, dass Sie der Elternteil oder Erziehungsberechtigte des unten angegebenen Kindes sind, welches jünger als %2$d Jahre ist.

 2. Wenn Sie dieses Formular ausfüllen, unterschreiben und zurücksenden, stimmen Sie der Nutzung der App durch Ihr Kind und der Erfassung, Verwendung und/oder Offenlegung der personenbezogenen Daten Ihres Kindes durch die App zu, gemäß diesem Formular und Norwegians Datenschutzrichtlinie unter https://www.ncl.com/about-us/privacy-policy.

 3. Jegliche Nutzung der App unterliegt ferner den Nutzungsbedingungen der App und allen anderen Bedingungen, Regeln oder Richtlinien, die Norwegian für die Nutzung der App geltend macht.

 4. Bitte beachten Sie, dass die App Kommunikationsfunktionen bietet (z. B. Chatten und Anrufen an Bord). Wenn die App zur Kommunikation genutzt wird, wird die Telefonnummer der App den anderen Parteien, mit denen der Nutzer kommuniziert, nicht angezeigt. Bitte klären Sie Ihr Kind darüber auf, dass die App-Telefonnummer ohne Ihre Zustimmung nicht an andere Personen übermittelt werden darf.

 5. Falls Ihr Kind externe Anrufe tätigen sollte, fallen Gebühren an; In diesem Fall ist die Kabine für die Zahlung dieser Gebühren verantwortlich.

 6. Die App generiert Datenanalysen, die in jeglicher Art in Norwegians alleinigem Ermessen (gemäß der Datenschutzrichtlinie) genutzt werden können, unter anderem (aber nicht ausschließlich) zum Zwecke der Verbesserung der Dienstleistungen durch Norwegian, der Verbesserung der App, des Kundenerlebnisses und so weiter."

"child_access_confirmation_legal_copy" : "Norwegian Cruise Line (Norwegian) ofrece una aplicación móvil (la Aplicación) que puede descargarse en un teléfono o dispositivo móvil. La Aplicación recoge información de sus usuarios. Norwegian exige que los padres o tutores legales de niños menores de %1$d años firmen este Formulario de consentimiento de los padres como condición para que el niño use la aplicación. 1. Usted reconoce y acepta que es el padre o tutor legal del menor de %2$d años que se menciona a continuación. 2. Al completar, firmar y entregar este formulario, usted autoriza el uso de la Aplicación por parte de su hijo, así como la recopilación, uso y/o divulgación por parte de la Aplicación y Norwegian de la información personal de su hijo a través de esta Aplicación, de acuerdo con este formulario y con la política de privacidad de Norwegian que puede consultarse en https://www.ncl.com/about-us/privacy-policy. 3. El uso de la Aplicación está sujeto a las condiciones de uso/condiciones de servicio de la Aplicación, y a cualquier otro tipo de condiciones, reglas o políticas que Norwegian aplique al uso de la Aplicación. 4. Tenga en cuenta que la aplicación ofrece funciones de comunicación (como la posibilidad de chatear y hacer llamadas a bordo).​​​​​​​ Cuando la Aplicación se usa para comunicarse, el número de teléfono de la Aplicación permanece oculto para las otras partes con las que el usuario se está comunicando. Aconseje a su hijo que no revele voluntariamente el número de teléfono de la Aplicación a nadie sin su consentimiento.

 5. Los niños pueden hacer llamadas fuera del barco con su dispositivo, pero se les cobrarán cargos o tarifas. Los cargos o tarifas que se cobren por hacer llamadas fuera del barco se aplicarán al camarote.

 6. La Aplicación generará análisis de datos que podrán utilizarse de cualquier manera a criterio exclusivo de Norwegian (de acuerdo con su política de privacidad), que incluye, entre otras cosas, la mejora de los servicios de Norwegian, el rendimiento de la Aplicación, la experiencia de los huéspedes, y cualquier otro tipo de uso."

 4. Observe que o Aplicativo fornece recursos de comunicação (como bate-papo e ligação a bordo). Quando o Aplicativo é usado para se comunicar, o número de telefone do Aplicativo fica oculto para outras partes com quem o usuário está se comunicando. Aconselhe o seu filho a não divulgar voluntariamente o número de telefone do Aplicativo para ninguém sem o seu consentimento.

 5. As crianças podem fazer chamadas para fora do navio com o dispositivo, mas isso resultará em cobranças ou taxas; a cabine é responsável por quaisquer cobranças ou taxas incorridas quando o dispositivo móvel fizer chamadas para fora do navio.

 6. O Aplicativo gerará análises de dados que podem ser usadas de qualquer maneira a critério exclusivo da Norwegian (de acordo com sua política de privacidade), incluindo, sem limitação, o aprimoramento dos serviços da Norwegian, o desempenho do Aplicativo, a experiência do passageiro e quaisquer outros usos."

playstore_details.title: Cruise Norwegian – Vacation, Plan & Connect
playstore_details.description:
Plan for your cruise vacation by booking dining, entertainment, and shore excursions in advance. Once onboard, access your trip schedule and Daily Activities, continue to book packages and utilize the app’s calling and texting feature package to chat with other guests aboard.

The Norwegian Cruise Line app is now available on all ships!

Key Features Include:

Retrieve reservation details, view your E-docs, prepare and save time boarding with mobile check-in, and access directions to the pier. 

Organize vacation itineraries by pre-booking activities in advance and while onboard i.e. shore excursions, dining reservations, entertainment, and make purchases including gifts (wine, flowers, and treats). 

Call and text guests aboard through the Norwegian Cruise Lines app including Group Chat*. 

View ship itineraries, port information, and daily activities.

Review your folio for onboard purchases in the app.

Check Latitude Reward points and learn more about our CruiseNext program. 
Review disembarkation information including immigration and easy walk-off details.


*Calling and Texting Package has a nominal one-time fee per person for making unlimited onboard calls and texts during your cruise.
playstore_details.summary: Use the app to plan your cruise in advance and as your onboard travel companion.
playstore_details.summaryHTML: Use the app to plan your cruise in advance and as your onboard travel companion.
